Hello, before  you read this you have to know this is  my first map, so pls dont be so strict.

So, this is a 1v1 map as you can see.
Its based on the detail, not on the gameplay so much.

i only used props, textures etc. from the source engine, there are no costume files.

I realy hope that i made everything right because, im new in mapping and at gamebanana!
